mutation ($payload:AppHealthCreateApplicationIntegrationInput!)

		id
		name
		description

		interfaceNumbers
		modality
		score
		documentations
	}
}

graphql.query:
query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	appHealthGetApplicationIntegrations (query: $query)
	{
		id
		name
		description
		interfaceNumbers
		modality
		score
		documentations
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	appHealthFindApplicationIntegration (query: $query)
	{
		id
		name
		description
		interfaceNumbers
		modality
		score
		documentations
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($id:ID)
{
	appHealthFindApplicationIntegrationById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		name
		description
		interfaceNumbers
		modality
		score
		documentations
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($payload:AppHealthUpdateApplicationIntegrationInput!)
{
	appHealthUpdateApplicationIntegration (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		name
		description
		interfaceNumbers
		modality
		score
		documentations
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($id:ID!)
{
	appHealthDeleteApplicationIntegrationById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		name
		description
		interfaceNumbers
		modality
		score
		documentations
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	appHealthDeleteApplicationIntegrations (query: $query)
	{
		id
		name
		description
		interfaceNumbers
		modality
		score
		documentations
		updatedAt
	}
}
